"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-08-04-parisolympics-pinnock-mcleod-advance-long-jump-final-gayle\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Wayne Pinnock and Carey McLeod are both through to the final of the men's long jump at the Olympic Games after Sunday morning's qualifying round at Stade de France.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Pinnock\", \"score\": 0.9999961552185839, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pinnock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Pinnock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_Pinnock\"}, {\"begin\": 18, \"end\": 23, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"score\": 0.989935956639144, \"rank\": 0.010137348531910829, \"text\": \"Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mariah_Carey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Jamaica's other representative, Tajay Gayle failed to advance.\", \"from\": 165, \"to\": 236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 174, \"end\": 181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.8485549309712006, \"rank\": 0.1761379533892669, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 206, \"end\": 217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tajay_Gayle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tajay Gayle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tajay_Gayle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tajay_Gayle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In what was a brutal qualifying round, none of the three Americans managed to advance with just two jumpers, defending champion Miltiadis Tentoglou of Greece, 8.32m (-0.6m/s), and Radek Juska of the Czech Republic, 8.15m (0.7m/s), managing to get the automatic qualifying mark of 8.15m.\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 389, \"end\": 395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.999528975258847, \"rank\": 0.0004592557017027503, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pinnock, the silver medallist at the World Championships last year, jumped 7.96m (1.6m/s), seventh best overall, while McLeod, the World Indoors bronze medallist, was 11th overall with 7.90m (-0.2m/s).\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 657, \"end\": 670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Indoor_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Indoors\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Indoor_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Indoor_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gayle's best mark was 7.78m (-1.3m/s), 19th overall.-Paul A Reid  Tags:  HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 729, \"end\": 734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\", \"score\": 0.9945542680128465, \"rank\": 0.005475550276568376, \"text\": \"Gayle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\"}]}]}"